<h4>Appliances</h4>
<p>Clean and empty all appliances. If you have the original boxes, then you are all set. However, if you do not, pack them in the closest size box you can find. Use wadded up packing paper to fill in any gaps around the appliances in the box. For larger appliances, remove any hoses and store them in the appliance (if possible). Tape the doors shut and tape the cords to the sides or back. Wrap them in moving blankets once they are on the moving truck.</p>
